data.description: Cabin on the Creek! Stop by and do some porch sittin’. This waterfront home has a magic all its own. You can’t help but relax and rid yourself of that hectic pace while you sit in your rocker on the back porch! This property is just under ½ acre with 172 ft of canal front. The dock has water and power and is just 6 homes in from the IntraCoastalWaterway with access to the Gulf of Mexico. It’s just a short distance to Nokomis Beach on Casey Key.  This cabin style cottage features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths and a 31 ft long lanai/porch along with an oversized garage that you may wish to use to store your boat.  It has an open floorplan with the dining room/living room off the kitchen. The home and shed both feature a long-lasting metal roof.  The home is cedar siding. There is plenty of room for a spacious swimming pool. This home is located near all that the local area has to offer along with easy access to Sarasota and its restaurants, shopping and the arts.  Or you may wish to start over and build a new home on this special waterfront property. Come take a look and sit awhile!
